app.livetv.ads.warn.description: 3rd party popups may show up in the video player, and if you try to close them new tabs will be opened in your browser. New opened tabs are not viruses, is just advertisement, we don't own such popup ads and at the time we don't have control over them. We are working to remove such annoying experience.
